---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about this blog and what we write about - web development, JavaScript, modern frameworks, and technology insights."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <article class="about-content">
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <p>
        Welcome! I'm a passionate developer who loves to share knowledge and experiences
        through writing. This blog is my personal space to document my journey, share
        insights, and connect with like-minded individuals.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Web Development</li>
        <li>JavaScript and TypeScript</li>
        <li>Modern frameworks and tools</li>
        <li>Best practices and design patterns</li>
        <li>Personal projects and experiments</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Thanks for visiting! This blog is a space to share knowledge, experiences, and
        insights about web development and technology. Feel free to explore the articles
        and learn something new.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content ul {
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
